<p>Renders a <code>&lt;th&gt;</code>. <code>scope</code> defaults to
  <code>"col"</code>. Use <code>scope="row"</code> for row headers.
  Add <code>classes: "table-col-numeric"</code> to right-align
  numeric columns. See the
  <a href="/components/table/">Table demo</a> for the composed
  example.</p>
